{"tid":291112,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N間openrice多好評但難食既食店","createTime":"2017-06-20T09:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T14:31:18.000Z","uid":114909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5aa817267f5d0375224582f09adc60e81a18aaf","tid":291112,"uid":114909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"相信大家都知openrice大部份都係打手post,<br />\n但好多人見到啲多好評既餐廳都會衝住去食,<br />\n希望大家一齊集思廣益防中伏,唔好浪費自己既時間同金錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-cafe-paradise-%E9%95%B7%E6%B2%99%E7%81%A3-%E8%A5%BF%E5%BC%8F-%E6%B2%99%E5%BE%8B-r492431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Fr-cafe-paradise-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2581%25A3-%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%25BC%258F-%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%25BE%258B-r492431&d=3BopktSSyOhqtll0OlwmBPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=952f0ff9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-cafe-paradise-%E9%95%B7%E6%B2%99%E7%81%A3-%E8%A5%BF%E5%BC%8F-%E6%B2%99%E5%BE%8B-r492431</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Cafe Paradise</strong><br />\n<br />\n呢間野好多人食,仲要BOOK位先食得,<br />\n先唔講野食,成間鋪超細同迫,隔離枱講野大聲少少已經聽唔到你對面果位講緊咩,<br />\n而食物方面咪就係同旺角樓上啲CAFE仔一樣,只係好過椰林閣少少,完全唔明點解OPENRICE咁多&quot;人&quot;會話好高質<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-%E7%89%9B%E6%B0%97-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%8F%9C-%E7%81%AB%E9%8D%8B-r433567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Fr-%25E7%2589%259B%25E6%25B0%2597-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%258F%259C-%25E7%2581%25AB%25E9%258D%258B-r433567&d=3BopktSSyOhqtll0OlwmBPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=1502ff31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-%E7%89%9B%E6%B0%97-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%8F%9C-%E7%81%AB%E9%8D%8B-r433567</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>牛気</strong><br />\n<br />\n呢間其實只係想用垃圾去形容就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自助果PART得啲垃圾丸同垃圾菜,比多少少錢就包海鮮,有垃圾青口同蝦果啲,但已經係講緊要比差唔多三百大元,點解比得二,三百唔係出邊啲唔係任食既鋪食?<br />\n仲有個湯又冇味,肉又唔係特別正,去吉野家都冇咁嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%8A%E4%BA%8C-%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%8F%9C-%E6%8B%89%E9%BA%B5-r435220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Fr-%25E5%258F%25A4%25E4%25BB%258A%25E4%25BA%258C-%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%258F%259C-%25E6%258B%2589%25E9%25BA%25B5-r435220&d=3BopktSSyOhqtll0OlwmBPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=16a85c6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%8A%E4%BA%8C-%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%8F%9C-%E6%8B%89%E9%BA%B5-r435220</a><br />\n<br />\n古今二<br />\n<br />\n港式日本餐廳,<br />\n佢連三文魚呢啲咁大路同油脂成份咁重既魚都可以冇味,可想而知啲料有幾新鮮,<br />\n同埋好多樣都係卷埋卷埋再吱沙律酱上去,感覺上依加啲香港人見到啲野食唔係屎型就會話性價比高同有創意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請接力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347d0964728befff6e5f6ffd9dbec774987e4c6c","tid":291112,"uid":90817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06b661c8dd38d61b5e7932bb4ff821271811a40a","tid":291112,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:04:49.000Z","msg":"呢間真係鬼撚到,開業不足兩年有74正評<br />\n我住附近日日都無乜人<br />\n我食過係唔好食嘅"},{"pid":"bdd30612577b6564a6122a2df849a623a79c559a","tid":291112,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-%E9%87%91%E6%A8%82%E8%BB%92%E9%9B%9E%E7%85%B2%E9%AD%9A%E9%8D%8B-%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92-%E5%B7%9D%E8%8F%9C-%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D-%E9%9B%9E%E7%85%B2-r445883/reviews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com